=== concepts_of_microsoft_sentinel ===

The Security Information Event Management (SIEM) and Security Orchestration Automated Response (SOAR)

Sentinel, intelligent security analytics

Cloud based

--- cycle of protection ---

--- Collect data by using data connectors ---
Links to microsoft platforms
3rd party data connectors are present as well
i.e. common event formats, syslog, rest-api

--- correlate alerts into incidents by using analytics rules ---

--- automate and orchestrate
Logic apps and connectors for:
* ServiceNow
* Jira
* Zendesk
* HTTP requests
* MS Teams
* Slack
* EntraID
* Defender for endpoint
* Defender for cloud apps

--- investigate the scope and root cause of security threats ---
